## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date sources and the potential bias in non-peer-reviewed articles. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of technology means that the findings may quickly become outdated as new communication tools and platforms emerge. Further research is recommended to explore the long-term effects of technology on communication skills and social interactions.